{"tid":1165143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(親中) 共和黨參議員: 要求罷免「特朗普」","createTime":"2019-05-21T14:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T03:57:30.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d4b1344f616656d35209b1b39d789b00301d18","tid":1165143,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"Justin Amash係共和黨議員, 唔係左膠.... 但佢係中國做生意. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6290741/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6290741%2F&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=424a4712\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6290741/</a><br />\n<br />\n第1位共和黨議員：川普行徑已符合「遭彈劾門檻」<br />\n編譯陳韻涵／綜合18日電 2019年05月19日 15:48 <br />\n<br />\n有意在2020年出馬挑戰川普的<strong>共和黨籍密西根州國會眾議員艾邁許(Justin Amash)</strong>18日推文表示，根據通俄案特別檢察官穆勒(Robert Mueller)的調查報告，川普總統「已觸及遭彈劾行徑」；<strong>艾邁許的指控讓他成為首位指稱川普行徑符合彈劾門檻的共和黨議員。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/powerpost/republicans-caught-between-trump-and-reluctance-to-penalize-rep-amash-after-impeachable-conduct-declaration/2019/05/20/717accbe-7b2c-11e9-a5b3-34f3edf1351e_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpowerpost%2Frepublicans-caught-between-trump-and-reluctance-to-penalize-rep-amash-after-impeachable-conduct-declaration%2F2019%2F05%2F20%2F717accbe-7b2c-11e9-a5b3-34f3edf1351e_story.html&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=2fc277ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/powerpost/republicans-caught-between-trump-and-reluctance-to-penalize-rep-amash-after-impeachable-conduct-declaration/2019/05/20/717accbe-7b2c-11e9-a5b3-34f3edf1351e_story.html</a><br />\n<br />\nOver the weekend, the pro-Trump One America News Network highlighted a Democratic opponent&rsquo;s past attacks on <strong> the congressman&rsquo;s family&rsquo;s business &mdash; a tool company with manufacturing interests in China &mdash; to suggest that Amash&rsquo;s impeachment stance was a self-interested attack motivated by Trump&rsquo;s trade policy.</strong>"},{"pid":"9e48bcfb96f071515d12ee56476a4106ec2b287d","tid":1165143,"uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"Justin Amash親中共紀實<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;v=u9gAOOGQqmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D5%26v%3Du9gAOOGQqmc&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=98ae7249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;v=u9gAOOGQqmc</a>"},{"pid":"c855d1f4caa7b8e4c09d14bda4e653e8a71da991","tid":1165143,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cbdb937d2dcb6d33db5051798d326d6459c2c2","tid":1165143,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e48bcfb96f071515d12ee56476a4106ec2b287d","tid":1165143,"uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"Justin Amash親中共紀實<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;v=u9gAOOGQqmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D5%26v%3Du9gAOOGQqmc&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=98ae7249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;v=u9gAOOGQqmc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/u9gAOOGQqmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu9gAOOGQqmc&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=fee54cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/u9gAOOGQqmc</a>"},{"pid":"06e6